name: ChatGPT (obiscr)
description: [项目级] This project is a plugin that supports ChatGPT running on JetBrains series IDE.。来源: https://github.com/obiscr/ChatGPT

genes.title: 项目概述
genes.content: This project is a plugin that supports ChatGPT running on JetBrains series IDE.

genes.title: 安装与快速开始
genes.content:
- Install using the IDE's built-in plugin system:

  <kbd>Settings/Preferences</kbd> > <kbd>Plugins</kbd> > <kbd>Marketplace</kbd> > <kbd>Search for "ChatGPT"</kbd> >
  <kbd>Install Plugin</kbd>
